{
  "design_notes": "We designed this Hard chart to feel fluid and driving. The intro uses eighth-note streams with light crossovers, stepping up the physical movement. During the build at Bar 28, we pulled back on the stream density to let the physical space feel sparse before the intense drop. The drop itself uses a heavy jumpstream with moderate crossovers and box movements to keep the player highly active and shifting across the pad. A tiny breather break at Bar 42 allows a moment of reset before hitting the final massive chorus/drop section starting at Bar 43, finishing with a sparse outro that naturally fades out the physical demand of the chart.",
